# and replay-verified with python-chess (v1 of this file had a hand-transcription
# error at ply 14 — Qxd6 not Bxd6 — which made every later move a different game;
# ELPH's UCI parser applies moves without legality checks, so it silently
# evaluated a garbage position. ALWAYS extract + replay-verify, never hand-copy.)
# Attackers on the long-castled Kb1: Qa4 (Chebyshev 3), Rc3 (Chebyshev 2),
# Rb8 (same file!), Nc4 + Nd5 (v3 ignores minors by design). a2 already vacated.
