# v3 static expectation: pressure = Q2+R1+R1 = 4 -> clamp 3; luft(b1) = 2 (a1,a2);
# shield missing 1 -> danger ~= 25 + TABLE[3,2]=45 = 70 against white, plus search
# propagation of the attack lines -> eval should read near 0 or NEGATIVE at d4/d5
# (vs the old +62/+122 serenity), telling white to defend while it still can.
